#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rebuilds the KService desktop file system configuration cache"
msgstr ""
"Bouwt opnieuw de systeemconfiguratiecache van de desktop-bestanden van "
"KService"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "Samenvatting"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">OPTIONS</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">OPTIES</replaceable></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschrijving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> builds binary cache of the data stored in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and &MIME; type <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses to find "
"plugins, applications and other services."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> bouwt de binaire cache van de gegevens "
"opgeslagen in <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> en &MIME;-type "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>-bestanden die het KService-"
"framework gebruikt om plug-ins, toepassingen en andere services te vinden."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService library uses this database to efficiently provide the "
"information requested of it."
msgstr ""
"De KService-bibliotheek gebruikt deze database om efficient de gevraagde "
"informatie ervan te leveren."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users do not normally need to run this application directly; KService will "
"run it if necessary, when any of the files whose data is cached are changed."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikers hoeven normaal deze toepassing niet direct te gebruiken; KService "
"zal het, indien nodig, uitvoeren wanneer een van de bestanden waarvan de "
"gegevens in de cache staat is gewijzigd."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opties"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "--global"
msgstr "--global"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
"currently only supported on &UNIX; systems."
msgstr ""
"Negeert elk door de gebruiker ingesteld bestand (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</"
"varname>). Dit wordt nu alleen ondersteunt in &UNIX;-systemen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noincremental"
msgstr "--noincremental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than using the existing cache and only updating the information that "
"has changed or been added, start with an empty cache. Ignored if <option>--"
"global</option> is set."
msgstr ""
"Anders dan de bestaande cache gebruiken en alleen de informatie bijwerken "
"als die is gewijzigd of er is iets toegevoegd, wordt gestart met een lege "
"cache. Wordt genegeerd als <option>--global</option> is ingesteld."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "--menutest"
msgstr "--menutest"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test the generation of the application menu database. Does not actually "
"build the cache."
msgstr ""
"Test de generatie van de menu-database voor toepassingen. Bouwt niet echt de "
"cache."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "--testmode"
msgstr "--testmode"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the QStandardPaths \"test mode\" to avoid interfering with user data. "
"This is intended for use with unit tests."
msgstr ""
"Gebruik de \"testmodus\" QStandardPaths om interferentie met "
"gebruikersgegevens te vermijden. Dit is bedoeld voor gebruik met tests van "
"eenheden."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"
msgstr "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track a menu ID for debugging."
msgstr "Track een menu-id voor debuggen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show author information."
msgstr "Auteurinformatie tonen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--license"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show license information."
msgstr "Licentie-informatie tonen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a brief help text."
msgstr "Een korte helptekst tonen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v , --version"
msgstr "-v , --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version information."
msgstr "Versie-informatie tonen"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files"
msgstr "Bestanden"

#. Tag: filename
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<varname>cachedir</varname>/ksycoca6_[lang]_[sha1-of-dirs]"
msgstr "<varname>cachedir</varname>/ksycoca6_[taal]_[sha1-van-mappen]"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService cache generated by <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. On &UNIX; "
"systems, <varname>cachedir</varname> is typically <filename class=\"directory"
"\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."
msgstr ""
"De KService cache gegenereerd door <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. Op "
"&UNIX;-systemen is <varname>cachedir</varname> typisch <filename class="
"\"directory\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>"

